{
  "chapter": 61,
  "chapter_summary": "庄襄王赛后召见项少龙和王翦，吕不韦在相国府设宴庆祝，赠三名齐国歌姬。项少龙推辞美色，吕不韦对他的品行更加敬重。宴席间商议赴赵生擒赵穆之事，吕不韦表示会向大王找借口掩护。关于荆俊被邱日升和国兴所伤一事，吕不韦承诺万事担当。次日滕翼和乌卓带精兵团战士赶回，三人决定以暴制暴前往武士行馆教训对方。途中遇到吕府侍卫追赶一名齐国女子善兰，滕翼出手相救。原来善兰是吕不韦所赠歌姬之一，因不愿为奴而逃跑。项少龙将善兰许配给滕翼，促成一段良缘。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本相近日获得齐人送来三名歌姬，均为不可多得的绝色美女，琴、棋、舞、曲无一不精，美女配英雄，本相就把她们转赠少龙、乌先生和蒙将军，万勿推辞。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "相爷好意，少龙心领了，邯郸之行，如箭在弦，势在必发，少龙不想因美色当前而分心，请相爷见谅。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那就由乌先生暂且保管，待少龙生擒赵穆回来后，再圆好梦。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_ao",
      "speaker_name": "蒙骜",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙准备何时赴赵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这里全是自己人，少龙直言无碍。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "待小俊康复后，立即起程。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我会和大王提此事的，到时随便找个借口，例如要你到某地办事，少龙将可神不知鬼不觉地潜往赵境去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小俊的仇不能不报，少龙准备怎样对付邱日升和国兴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "这事情如闹大了，大王会否不高兴呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "放心吧！刚才本相曾和大王提及此事，他也非常不满邱日升的卑鄙手段，少龙尽管放手去做，万事有本相担当。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "少龙晓得怎样做的了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "得少龙如此佳婿，不但是廷芳之福，亦是乌家之幸，若非少龙，我们在秦国哪有目前如此风光。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "待少龙把赵穆生擒回来后，少龙至紧要向大王提出为爹在咸阳建一个宏伟的衣冠冢，想起他老人家尸骨无存，我便……唉！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们的确想要小俊的命。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "你们到邯郸去，绝不能没我的份儿。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "那你就好好睡个觉吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "唯一的方法，是以暴制暴，否则迟早会有另一次同样的事情发生。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "我们还要公然行事，尽量把事情闹大，让所有人都知道我们乌家不是好欺负的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事不宜迟，我很久没有活动筋骨了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "那不若立即起程，教训完那些蠢材后，我们还有时间吃顿丰盛的午饭。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "善兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀了我吧！我怎也不回去的了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "我们的事你也敢管，活得不耐烦哩！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_shan_lan",
      "text": "姑娘起来吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "善兰",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "你斗不过他们的，走吧！否则会连累你们。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_shan_lan",
      "text": "我滕翼从不怕任何人，大不了是一死！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lang",
      "speaker_name": "张郎",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这位不是项太傅吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lang",
      "text": "这是怎么一回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lang",
      "speaker_name": "张郎",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人叫张郎，是吕相国府的人，刚才奉相爷之命把两名齐女送往贵府，岂知竟给此女中途溜走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lang",
      "text": "原来是一场误会，好了！这齐女就当交收完成，你们可以回去复命了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lang",
      "speaker_name": "张郎",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还有一个，在后面的马车上……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lang",
      "text": "那位就麻烦诸位大哥送往舍下好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_lan",
      "text": "怎样称呼姑娘呢？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "善兰",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我叫善兰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_shan_lan",
      "text": "为何来到咸阳还要逃走？在这里刑法森严，以五家为伍，十家为什，不准擅自迁居，互相监督，一家犯法，十家得连坐同罪，知情不举的腰斩，谁敢把你藏起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "善兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "我准备一死了之，哪管得这么多。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_lan",
      "text": "现在善姑娘既知是要到我们家来，还要逃走吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "善兰",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我不知道！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_lan",
      "text": "这样吧！我给姑娘两个选择，一是由我们派人把姑娘送回齐国与家人团聚，一是你嫁给我这兄弟滕翼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "善兰",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小女子早无家可归了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "如此就恭喜滕兄。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！她本应是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "说这种话就不当我是兄弟。唉！滕兄肯再接受幸福生活，我高兴得差点想掉泪呢！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天似乎不大适合去找邱日升晦气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "先回府再说吧！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    }
  ],
